                     <interp inst="t18280911-11-off56" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280911-11-cd57" type="crimeDate">5th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-11-off56 t18280911-11-cd57"></join>, 1 handkerchief, value 5s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280911-11-victim156" type="victimName">
                        Richard Edward 
                        Tippet
                     <interp inst="t18280911-11-victim156" type="surname" value="Tippet"></interp>
